CatDescriptText: Seated from left: William Goode, unknown, Joe Lawfton, George Charlton, Rev. Amos Prakens, Rev. James B. Cayce, and Ralph Barnett; second row: Lorenzo Hill, unknown, Bob Smith, Dr. Leon Ford, two unknown men, John Smith, Moses Edwards James Greenlee, Russell Washington, unknown, Arthur Burt, and four unknown men; third row: unknown, Alan James, three unknown men, Fred Gladney, unknown, Joe McCormack, Rev James B. Brown, and unknown.
